<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About • PostNest</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
</head>
<script>
  function toggleMenu() {
    document.getElementById("mobileMenu").classList.toggle("hidden");
  }
</script>
<body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700">

<nav class="bg-white shadow-sm sticky top-0 z-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
      <img 
        src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/616/616408.png"
        alt="PostNest Logo"
        class="w-9 h-9"
      />
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-600">PostNest</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="hidden sm:flex gap-3">
<a href="/home"
  class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition
  <%= currentPath === '/home'
    ? 'bg-indigo-600 text-white'
    : 'border border-indigo-600 text-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-50'
  %>">
  Home
</a>

        <a href="/profile"
  class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition
  <%= currentPath === '/profile'
    ? 'bg-indigo-600 text-white'
    : 'border border-indigo-600 text-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-50'
  %>">
  Profile
</a>

      <a href="/about"
  class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition
  <%= currentPath === '/about'
    ? 'bg-indigo-600 text-white'
    : 'border border-indigo-600 text-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-50'
  %>">
  About Us
</a>

      <a href="/login"
  class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition
  <%= currentPath === '/login'
    ? 'bg-indigo-600 text-white'
    : 'border border-indigo-600 text-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-50'
  %>">
  Login
</a>

      <a href="/index"
  class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition
  <%= currentPath === '/index'
    ? 'bg-indigo-600 text-white'
    : 'border border-indigo-600 text-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-50'
  %>">
  Register
</a>

    </div>
    <button onclick="toggleMenu()" class="sm:hidden">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-indigo-600" fill="none"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
          d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16" />
      </svg>
    </button>
  </div>
  <div id="mobileMenu" class="hidden sm:hidden bg-white border-t">
<a href="/home"
  class="block px-6 py-3 transition
  <%= currentPath === '/home'
    ? 'bg-indigo-600 text-white'
    : 'text-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-50'
  %>">
  Home
</a>

    <a href="/profile"
  class="block px-6 py-3 transition
  <%= currentPath === '/profile'
    ? 'bg-indigo-600 text-white'
    : 'text-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-50'
  %>">
  Profile
</a>

    <a href="/about"
  class="block px-6 py-3 transition
  <%= currentPath === '/about'
    ? 'bg-indigo-600 text-white'
    : 'text-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-50'
  %>">
  About Us
</a>

    <a href="/login"
  class="block px-6 py-3 transition
  <%= currentPath === '/login'
    ? 'bg-indigo-600 text-white'
    : 'text-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-50'
  %>">
  Login
</a>

    <a href="/index"
  class="block px-6 py-3 transition
  <%= currentPath === '/index'
    ? 'bg-indigo-600 text-white'
    : 'text-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-50'
  %>">
  Register
</a>

  </div>
</nav>

  <section class="py-20 shadow-sm bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 via-cyan-500 to-teal-500 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-indigo-700 mb-4">About PostNest</h1>
      <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
        A modern social platform designed to share thoughts, ideas, and moments — 
        simply, beautifully, and securely.
      </p>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-indigo-500 mx-auto mt-6 rounded-full"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          PostNest was built with one clear goal: to create a safe and minimal space 
          where users can express themselves freely. In a world full of noise, 
          PostNest focuses on meaningful content, simplicity, and authentic interaction.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          Whether you want to share daily thoughts, connect with others, or simply 
          explore ideas from the community, PostNest gives your words a place to belong.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow">
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-indigo-500 text-xl">✔</span>
            Clean and modern user experience
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-indigo-500 text-xl">✔</span>
            Secure authentication and privacy
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-indigo-500 text-xl">✔</span>
            Community-driven content sharing
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-indigo-500 text-xl">✔</span>
            Responsive and accessible design
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">
        Why Choose PostNest?
      </h2>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border bg-gray-50">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-indigo-600">User-Focused</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Built keeping simplicity and usability in mind for a smooth experience.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border bg-gray-50">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-indigo-600">Fast & Secure</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Modern authentication, secure sessions, and efficient backend design.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border bg-gray-50">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-indigo-600">Community First</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Engage with posts, like content, and explore ideas shared by others.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <img
        src="/images/uploads/vansh.jpg"
        alt="Founder"
        class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto rounded-full mb-6"
      />

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Vansh Bisht</h2>
      <p class="text-indigo-600 mb-4">Founder & Developer — PostNest</p>

      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Hi, I’m Vansh Bisht — a Computer Science student and passionate web developer.
        PostNest is a personal project created to strengthen my full-stack skills and
        build a real-world social platform using modern technologies.
        <br /><br />
        This project reflects my interest in clean UI, scalable backend systems,
        and meaningful digital experiences.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-indigo-600 py-12">
    <div class="text-center text-white">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Join the PostNest Community</h2>
      <p class="mb-4 text-indigo-100">
        Share your thoughts. Connect with people. Build your nest.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/profile"
        class="inline-block bg-white text-indigo-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-100 transition"
      >
        Go to Profile
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
